4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals looking to become cybersecurity specialists from scratch. Over 16 weeks, students participate in 3 live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 16. The program includes foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with advanced topics such as cloud security, penetration testing, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001. No prior experience is necessary, and the curriculum is available in English and Spanish. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop